data.description: Like-new, this masterful Dahl Built Home sits on a quarter-acre lot in Fruita’s Orchard Ridge and combines modern luxury with comforting amenities. The sleek design sets this home apart – from the multiple ceiling heights, tray ceilings designs, and clean eye-catching features. Natural lights bathes each room in warmth, and the waterfall granite island and glass tile backsplash in the kitchen create an inviting and elegant space. Functionality comes to life with the 8x8 walk-in pantry, walk-in closets in each bedroom, and the custom built-in storage throughout. The home’s primary suite is a luxurious retreat with its 5pc en-suite featuring a soaking tub before a glass-tiled wall feature along with a tiled walk-in shower. The expansive patio plus a custom gas fire pit in the private backyard create a relaxing and serene environment with surrounding views. Professionally landscaped and with a shed and RV parking, this showstopper is a must see!
